= Introduction =

This document describes various aspects of sort4j usage

= Getting sort4j =

There's two ways to get sort4j

  * Download it from http://code.google.com/p/sort4j/downloads/list page
  * Get sort4j from maven. Sort4j isn't a part of maven central repository, but you could use this one: http://java.iponweb.net/maven2/thirdparty/

= Defining sort4j task =

For creating sort4j task use sort4j.SortingTask class. It implements builder interface. Also you could user SortingTask.textFormat() that creates a skeleton for task which sort text files

= Sorting =

Just create an instance of sort4j.Sorter class and call sort() method. Currently, only ne implementation is available: sort4j.MergeSorter